人權法案的時候，<br />\n千祈唔好放棄twitter戰線呀！<br />\n仲有英國話今日會講英女王會講英國版magnitsky Act！<br />\n依家係重要關頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定要一人一twitter!!!!!!<br />\n一路retweet一路去集會！"},{"pid":"5a4d39ba399257ee785e3b4e44321348cbec5046","tid":1653071,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808e95c69f557af20cc01418ac70f74a1743b0aa","tid":1653071,"uid":61520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9c005c4ad0f0b202e432a029987719e1a042a0e2","tid":1653071,"uid":91432,"like":4,"dislike":68,"score":-64,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"香港人？<br />\n<br />\n好冇尊嚴咖喎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:34:58.000Z","msg":"今晚就拎樽鹽出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e25fbc8f5d964d298e92d9ea765eee093cfab10","tid":1653071,"uid":282435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"咁不如話，「我們都是美國人」"},{"pid":"b927fbe01f5e0932fbaaa74477b70b5e40216c90","tid":1653071,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e25fbc8f5d964d298e92d9ea765eee093cfab10","tid":1653071,"uid":282435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"咁不如話，「我們都是美國人」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:35:12.000Z","msg":"Good Idea"},{"pid":"311b70ff13239a024791b4865d3f583f2f53ace7","tid":1653071,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c005c4ad0f0b202e432a029987719e1a042a0e2","tid":1653071,"uid":91432,"like":4,"dislike":68,"score":-64,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"香港人？<br />\n<br />\n好冇尊嚴咖喎。"},